<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>CPA 2027 考试大纲 · 知识点全览</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #f2f2f7;
  --card: #ffffff;
  --text: #1c1c1e;
  --text2: #636366;
  --text3: #8e8e93;
  --blue: #007aff;
  --green: #34c759;
  --orange: #ff9500;
  --red: #ff3b30;
  --purple: #af52de;
  --teal: #5ac8fa;
  --pink: #ff2d55;
  --indigo: #5856d6;
  --separator: rgba(60,60,67,0.12);
  --card-radius: 12px;
  --group-radius: 14px;
  --safe-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px);
}
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { font-size:16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', 'SF Pro Display', 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.47;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  padding-bottom: calc(20px + var(--safe-bottom));
}

/* ─── Header ─── */
.header {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(242,242,247,0.82);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
  backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--separator);
  padding: 12px 16px 8px;
}
.header-top { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:8px; }
.header h1 { font-size:28px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.5px; }
.header .subtitle { font-size:13px; color:var(--text3); margin-top:2px; }
.header .badge-group { display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:8px; }
.badge {
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:4px;
  font-size:11px; font-weight:600; padding:3px 8px;
  border-radius:6px; line-height:1.4;
}
.badge.hot { background:rgba(255,59,48,0.12); color:var(--red); }
.badge.new { background:rgba(0,122,255,0.12); color:var(--blue); }
.badge.star { background:rgba(255,149,0,0.12); color:var(--orange); }

/* ─── Search ─── */
.search-bar {
  position:relative; margin-top:10px;
}
.search-bar input {
  width:100%; height:36px; border:none; border-radius:10px;
  background:rgba(118,118,128,0.12); padding:0 12px 0 32px;
  font-size:15px; color:var(--text); outline:none;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.search-bar input::placeholder { color:var(--text3); }
.search-bar svg { position:absolute; left:10px; top:50%; transform:translateY(-50%); color:var(--text3); }

/* ─── Tab bar (subjects) ─── */
.tabs-wrap {
  overflow-x:auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;
  scrollbar-width:none; padding:12px 0 0;
}
.tabs-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
.tabs {
  display:flex; gap:8px; padding:0 16px; min-width:max-content;
}
.tab-btn {
  flex-shrink:0; padding:7px 14px; border-radius:20px;
  font-size:14px; font-weight:500; border:none; cursor:pointer;
  background:rgba(118,118,128,0.08); color:var(--text2);
  transition:all 0.25s ease; white-space:nowrap;
}
.tab-btn.active { background:var(--blue); color:#fff; font-weight:600; }

/* ─── Content ─── */
.content { padding:12px 16px; }
.subject-section { display:none; animation:fadeUp 0.3s ease; }
.subject-section.active { display:block; }
@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

/* ─── Section header ─── */
.section-header {
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  margin:16px 0 8px; padding:0 4px;
}
.section-icon {
  width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:8px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:16px; color:#fff; flex-shrink:0;
}
.section-header h2 { font-size:20px; font-weight:700; }
.section-header .count { font-size:12px; color:var(--text3); margin-left:auto; }

/* ─── Knowledge cards ─── */
.knowledge-group {
  background:var(--card); border-radius:var(--group-radius);
  overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:12px;
  box-shadow:0 0.5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.knowledge-item {
  display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px;
  padding:12px 14px;
  border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--separator);
  cursor:pointer; transition:background 0.15s;
}
.knowledge-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.knowledge-item:active { background:rgba(0,0,0,0.03); }
.knowledge-item.expanded { background:rgba(0,122,255,0.02); }

.k-dot {
  width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--text3); margin-top:7px; flex-shrink:0;
}
.k-dot.hot { background:var(--red); }
.k-dot.new { background:var(--blue); }

.k-body { flex:1; min-width:0; }
.k-title { font-size:15px; font-weight:500; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.k-title .tag {
  font-size:10px; font-weight:600; padding:1px 5px;
  border-radius:4px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;
}
.k-title .tag.hot { background:rgba(255,59,48,0.1); color:var(--red); }
.k-title .tag.new { background:rgba(0,122,255,0.1); color:var(--blue); }
.k-title .tag.star { background:rgba(255,149,0,0.1); color:var(--orange); }
.k-title .tag.hot::before { content:'🔥 '; }
.k-title .tag.new::before { content:'✨ '; }
.k-title .tag.star::before { content:'⭐ '; }

.k-detail {
  font-size:13px; color:var(--text2); margin-top:4px;
  line-height:1.5; display:none;
}
.knowledge-item.expanded .k-detail { display:block; }
.k-sub { padding:2px 0 2px 12px; border-left:2px solid var(--separator); margin-top:6px; }
.k-sub p { font-size:13px; color:var(--text2); padding:2px 0; }

.k-arrow {
  color:var(--text3); font-size:12px; margin-top:4px;
  transition:transform 0.2s; flex-shrink:0;
}
.knowledge-item.expanded .k-arrow { transform:rotate(90deg); }

/* ─── Stats ─── */
.stats-row {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:8px;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}
.stat-card {
  background:var(--card); border-radius:var(--group-radius);
  padding:12px; text-align:center;
  box-shadow:0 0.5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.stat-card .num { font-size:24px; font-weight:700; }
.stat-card .label { font-size:11px; color:var(--text3); margin-top:2px; }

/* ─── Legend ─── */
.legend {
  display:flex; gap:12px; padding:8px 4px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.legend-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; font-size:12px; color:var(--text2); }
.legend-dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; }

/* ─── Quick links ─── */
.quick-section { margin-bottom:16px; }
.quick-section h3 { font-size:13px; color:var(--text3); font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px; margin-bottom:8px; padding:0 4px; }
.quick-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:8px; }
.quick-card {
  background:var(--card); border-radius:var(--group-radius);
  padding:14px; text-align:center; cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  box-shadow:0 0.5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.quick-card:active { transform:scale(0.97); }
.quick-card .icon { font-size:24px; margin-bottom:4px; }
.quick-card .name { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; }
.quick-card .desc { font-size:11px; color:var(--text3); margin-top:2px; }

/* ─── Footer ─── */
.footer {
  text-align:center; padding:20px 16px; font-size:12px; color:var(--text3);
}

/* ─── Scroll to top ─── */
.scroll-top {
  position:fixed; bottom:24px; right:16px;
  width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); border:none;
  box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  cursor:pointer; opacity:0; transform:translateY(10px);
  transition:all 0.3s; z-index:99;
  -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(10px); backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}
.scroll-top.show { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
.scroll-top:active { transform:scale(0.9); }

/* ─── Search highlight ─── */
mark { background:rgba(255,204,0,0.35); color:inherit; border-radius:2px; padding:0 1px; }

/* ─── Print ─── */
@media print {
  .header, .tabs-wrap, .scroll-top, .search-bar { display:none !important; }
  .subject-section { display:block !important; page-break-inside:avoid; }
  body { background:#fff; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header -->
<div class="header" id="header">
  <div class="header-top">
    <div>
      <h1>CPA 2027</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">注册会计师全国统一考试 · 大纲知识点全览</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="badge-group">
    <span class="badge hot">🔥 常考重点</span>
    <span class="badge new">✨ 新增知识点</span>
    <span class="badge star">⭐ 核心考点</span>
  </div>
  <div class="search-bar">
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
    <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="搜索知识点..." oninput="doSearch(this.value)">
  </div>
  <div class="tabs-wrap">
    <div class="tabs" id="tabBar">
      <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('overview')">总览</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('accounting')">会计</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('audit')">审计</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('tax')">税法</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('law')">经济法</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('fm')">财务成本管理</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('strategy')">公司战略</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('comprehensive')">综合阶段</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Content -->
<div class="content">

<!-- ═══════════ 总览 ═══════════ -->
<div class="subject-section active" id="sec-overview">
  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="num" style="color:var(--blue)">6</div><div class="label">专业阶段科目</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="num" style="color:var(--red)">186</div><div class="label">知识模块</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="num" style="color:var(--green)">5</div><div class="label">综合阶段卷</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--red)"></div>常考重点</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--blue)"></div>2027新增/变动</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--orange)"></div>核心考点</div>
  </div>
  <div class="quick-section">
    <h3>专业阶段 · 六科速览</h3>
    <div class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('accounting')"><div class="icon">📒</div><div class="name">会计</div><div class="desc">30章 · 基础核心</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('audit')"><div class="icon">🔍</div><div class="name">审计</div><div class="desc">23章 · 难度最高</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('tax')"><div class="icon">💰</div><div class="name">税法</div><div class="desc">14章 · 细节繁多</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('law')"><div class="icon">⚖️</div><div class="name">经济法</div><div class="desc">12章 · 记忆为主</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('fm')"><div class="icon">📊</div><div class="name">财务成本管理</div><div class="desc">21章 · 公式密集</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('strategy')"><div class="icon">🎯</div><div class="name">公司战略</div><div class="desc">7章 · 理解为主</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="quick-section">
    <h3>综合阶段</h3>
    <div class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('comprehensive')"><div class="icon">📋</div><div class="name">试卷一</div><div class="desc">会计审计税法</div></div>
      <div class="quick-card" onclick="switchTab('comprehensive')"><div class="icon">📋</div><div class="name">试卷二</div><div class="desc">财管战略经济法</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════ 会计 ═══════════ -->
<div class="subject-section" id="sec-accounting">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-icon" style="background:var(--blue)">📒</div>
    <h2>会计</h2>
    <span class="count">30章</span>
  </div>

  <div class="knowledge-group">
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第1章 总论 <span class="tag hot">常考</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 会计基本假设与会计基础</p><p>• 会计信息质量要求（可靠性、相关性、可理解性等8项）</p><p>• 会计要素及其确认与计量</p><p>• 会计计量属性（历史成本、重置成本、可变现净值、现值、公允价值）</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第2章 会计政策、会计估计及其变更和差错更正 <span class="tag hot">常考</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 会计政策及其变更（追溯调整法）</p><p>• 会计估计及其变更（未来适用法）</p><p>• 前期差错更正（追溯重述法）</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot new"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第3章 存货 <span class="tag new">2027变动</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 存货的确认和初始计量</p><p>• 发出存货的计量（先进先出法、加权平均法等）</p><p>• 期末存货的计量（成本与可变现净值孰低）</p><p>• 存货的清查盘点</p><p class="mark-new">📌 2027新增：存货减值测试中关于可持续发展相关成本的处理</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第4章 固定资产 <span class="tag star">核心</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 固定资产的确认和初始计量</p><p>• 固定资产的后续计量（折旧方法、后续支出）</p><p>• 固定资产的处置</p><p>• 固定资产的清查</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第5章 无形资产</div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 无形资产的确认和初始计量</p><p>• 内部研究开发费用的确认和计量</p><p>• 无形资产的后续计量</p><p>• 无形资产的处置和报废</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第6章 投资性房地产</div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 投资性房地产的确认和初始计量</p><p>• 投资性房地产的后续计量（成本模式与公允价值模式）</p><p>• 投资性房地产的转换和处置</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第7章 长期股权投资与合营安排 <span class="tag star">核心</span><span class="tag hot">常考</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 长期股权投资的初始计量</p><p>• 长期股权投资的后续计量（成本法与权益法）</p><p>• 长期股权投资核算方法的转换</p><p>• 合营安排（共同经营与合营企业）</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第8章 资产减值</div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 资产减值概述</p><p>• 资产可收回金额的计量</p><p>• 资产减值损失的确认与计量</p><p>• 资产组的认定及减值处理</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第9章 负债 <span class="tag hot">常考</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 流动负债（应付职工薪酬、应交税费等）</p><p>• 非流动负债（应付债券、长期借款等）</p><p>• 借款费用</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第10章 职工薪酬 <span class="tag hot">常考</span><span class="tag new">2027变动</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 设定受益计划的会计处理</p><p>• 短期薪酬、离职后福利、辞退福利</p><p class="mark-new">📌 2027新增：离职后福利中关于养老金改革新规的衔接处理</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第11章 借款费用</div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 借款费用的确认</p><p>• 借款费用资本化金额的确定</p><p>• 借款费用资本化的暂停与停止</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第12章 股份支付 <span class="tag star">核心</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 以权益结算的股份支付</p><p>• 以现金结算的股份支付</p><p>• 股份支付条件的修改与取消</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
      <div class="k-body">
        <div class="k-title">第13章 或有事项 <span class="tag hot">常考</span></div>
        <div class="k-detail"><div class="k-sub"><p>• 或有事项的确认和计量</p><p>• 或有事项会计的具体应用（预计负债、或有负债、或有资产）</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="k-arrow">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-item" onclick="toggleItem(this)">
      <div class="k-dot hot"></div>
